"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-09-team-gb-teen-dubbed-the-terminator-clinches-historic-olympic-gold-21394428\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Team GB teenager Toby 'The Terminator' Roberts has clinched a historic medal at theParisOlympics, with the nation's first in sport climbing.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 140, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 7, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9990974218592383, \"rank\": 0.000857755435164871, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 17, \"end\": 21, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Animorphs\", \"score\": 0.8817205399573588, \"rank\": 0.13414538951533117, \"text\": \"Toby\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Animorphs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Animorphs\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 19-year-old from Surrey secured gold in the men's combined event after a dramatic slip-up fromJapan's Sorato Anraku, who was forced to settle for silver.\", \"from\": 142, \"to\": 299, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 163, \"end\": 169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Surrey\", \"score\": 0.9680930456793818, \"rank\": 0.03284473273771782, \"text\": \"Surrey\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Surrey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Surrey\"}, {\"begin\": 255, \"end\": 261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tomohiro_Anraku\", \"score\": 0.9999999994990958, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anraku\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tomohiro_Anraku\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tomohiro_Anraku\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Roberts was left in utter disbelief and had his head in his hands as he wrote his name into British Olympic history at the 2024 Paris Games.\", \"from\": 301, \"to\": 441, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 393, \"end\": 400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.7871711129152158, \"rank\": 0.2657791730878887, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am just lost for words,' a gobsmacked Roberts told theBBC.\", \"from\": 443, \"to\": 504, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'To find out that I had got the gold in that moment was truly incredible.\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 578, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'[Anraku] is just an incredibly strong climber and it is insane how strong he is.\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 661, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He looked a little nervous but he is incredibly strong.\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 717, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have been training for this moment my whole life.\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 771, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To say it has not sunk in is an understatement.\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 819, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I imagine later it will be a flood of emotions.\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 869, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is a goal I have been training towards this for like 10 years.'\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 936, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked how 'Toby Roberts, Olympic gold medallist' sound to him, the teen added: 'It sounds incredible!'\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 1040, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 949, \"end\": 953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Animorphs\", \"score\": 0.8817205399573588, \"rank\": 0.13414538951533117, \"text\": \"Toby\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Animorphs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Animorphs\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Anraku looked firmly set for gold having entered the event as the favourite and he did not seem tired or fatigued as he started climbing the wall like Spiderman.\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1203, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1042, \"end\": 1048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tomohiro_Anraku\", \"score\": 0.9999999994990958, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anraku\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tomohiro_Anraku\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tomohiro_Anraku\"}, {\"begin\": 1193, \"end\": 1202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spider-Man\", \"score\": 0.9999996813124251, \"rank\": 2.856886081911823e-07, \"text\": \"Spiderman\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spider-Man\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spider-Man\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many felt Anraku, dubbed 'The Octopus', would be unbeatable but he slipped on his ascent up the 15m wall in dramatic scenes.\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1329, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1215, \"end\": 1221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tomohiro_Anraku\", \"score\": 0.9999999994990958, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anraku\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tomohiro_Anraku\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tomohiro_Anraku\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Japanese star took silver, while the bronze medal went to Austrian rock climber Jakob Schubert.\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1430, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1335, \"end\": 1343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.987847648045715, \"rank\": 0.011826183715055203, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1393, \"end\": 1401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austrians\", \"score\": 0.9646953870706414, \"rank\": 0.027101713016271338, \"text\": \"Austrian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austrians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austrians\"}, {\"begin\": 1415, \"end\": 1429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Schubert\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jakob Schubert\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Schubert\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Schubert\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Finishing ahead of both of them was Britain's latest Olympics star, Roberts, who trained on a climbing wall in the garden of his family home ahead of the Games.\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1592, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1468, \"end\": 1475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9869664544532912, \"rank\": 0.00968030278539787, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Britain's Hamish McArthur, meanwhile, also took part in the men's combined event and finished fifth.\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1694, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1594, \"end\": 1601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9869664544532912, \"rank\": 0.00968030278539787, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Olympic water polo player left bloody after gruesome eye injury  ArrowMORE:'Drunk' Olympic wrestler arrested for sexual assault in Paris  ArrowMORE:Paris Olympics shooter dramatically collapses during press conference  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 2035, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1837, \"end\": 1842, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999586439126, \"rank\": 4.13561164152816e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"